IS  - 2
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - The relationship between self and superior ratings of performance was investigated. The difference between the two ratings was found to be related to the subordinate's self-esteem and his satisfaction with his supervision. These results are discussed in terms of the usefulness of self-ratings in organizational decision making.
